name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hubspot Print Contact Page CSS adjustments

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hubspot contact pages get truncated when you print or save to PDF. This extension makes it work by adjusting some CSS properties.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hubspot contact pages get truncated when you try to print or save it to PDF. It seems to print only one page. This extension makes it work by adjusting some CSS properties, hiding some elements like navigation, headers, titles and UI elements.
